Easy up.

This is a very short manual for the easy_up scroll. The command listed below
can be placed anywhere in the text in the following manner:

^fmediapoint^^s20^Text

This example shows the word 'Text' in the mediapoint size 20. The one restriction
is that there can be only one font per line.

f - set font
a - set allignment l,r and m
c - set color xxx
v - set speed
m - set middle
g - set gapsize between character role
t - set shadow type f for filled other for non filled
d - set shadow depth
i - set spacing between lines
s - set font size
